text: Ærest of Mylebroce on Cuceles hylle.
Of ðære stræt on ðone ealdan wæg ðurh ðone graf & swa on ðone smalan pæð ofer ða stræt on þone ealdan weg & swa andlang weges on Atange, <earh>.
Of ðam beorge suþ on ða ealdan wale.
Swa on corf getes westran cotan.
Of ðam cotan suþ be wale on ðære dice hyrnan.
And swa west be dic on oþre hyrnan swa suþ be dic on ðære mæde hyrnan.
And ðær west be dic on oþre mæde hyrnan.
And swa suþ andlang dic on halgan wyl.
Of halgan wylle west be dic on ða clæian lane.
Of ðære clæian lane on Mylebroc adun be streame eft of Mylebroce on Cuceles hylle.
